OL,3,CWhat do Reeves' colossal Budget tax
OL,4,Cchanges mean for the economy?
OL,6,FITV News' Business and Economics
OL,7,FEditor Joel Hills' assesses the big
OL,8,Fmeasures announced in Rachel Reeve's
OL,9,Fhistoric Budget
OL,11,FWe knew taxes were going to rise.
OL,12,FLabour set out plans to raise more
OL,13,Fthan #8 billion a year in its
OL,14,Fmanifesto.
OL,16,FThat was made up of closing tax
OL,17,Floopholes for non-doms, VAT being
OL,18,Flevied on private schools and a
OL,19,Fwindfall tax on oil and gas companies.
