OL,3,CWhat do Reeves' colossal Budget tax
OL,4,Cchanges mean for the economy?
OL,6,FThe Labour manifesto clearly promised
OL,7,F"no additional tax rises" beyond these.
OL,9,FThis is what we got: a really chunky
OL,10,Fand significant increase to National
OL,11,FInsurance for employers - rising from
OL,12,F13% to 15% from April 2025. That alone
OL,13,Fwill take #25 billion off borrowing by
OL,14,Fthe end of the next forecast,
OL,15,Faccording to the Office for Budget
OL,16,FResponsibility (OBR).
