OL,3,CWhat do Reeves' colossal Budget tax
OL,4,Cchanges mean for the economy?
OL,6,FThere were increases too for capital
OL,7,Fgains tax, which will rise to 24% at
OL,8,Fthe upper rate and 10% at the lower
OL,9,Frate, while farmers will feel the
OL,10,Fbrunt of inheritance tax being
OL,11,Fintroduced for the first time on
OL,12,Fagricultural land from 2027.
OL,14,FChancellor Rachel Reeves, meanwhile,
OL,15,Fhas committed to extend the threshold
OL,16,Ffreeze of #325,000 for inheritance tax
OL,17,Fthrough to the end of 2030.
OL,19,FAll in all, that's a total tax rise of
OL,20,F#40 billion.
