OL,3,CWhat do Reeves' colossal Budget tax
OL,4,Cchanges mean for the economy?
OL,6,FMr Hughes told broadcasters: "It
OL,7,Fdoesn't involve previous ministers. It
OL,8,Fdoesn't mention previous ministers. It
OL,9,Fwas a review into the institutional
OL,10,Frelationship between the OBR and the
OL,11,FTreasury and the preparation of our
OL,12,FMarch 2024 economic and fiscal outlook.
OL,14,F"In the course of the review we
OL,15,Funcovered #9.5 billion worth of
OL,16,Fspending pressures that the Treasury
OL,17,Fwas aware of at the time, but that
OL,18,Fweren't disclosed to the OBR."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
