OL,3,CWhat do Reeves' colossal Budget tax
OL,4,Cchanges mean for the economy?
OL,6,FIt's fine in the short term. There is
OL,7,Fa boost, but beyond 2027, actually,
OL,8,Fthe forecasts are really pretty
OL,9,Fdepressing.
OL,11,FGrowth is set to fall from 1.8%
OL,12,Fannually to 1.5%, then stay at 1.5%
OL,13,Fthe next year.
OL,15,FIn terms of the increase in growth,
OL,16,Fthe OBR concludes that the policies
OL,17,Fannounced today temporarily boost
OL,18,Foutput in the near term.
